dct_title_s: Map of Harz Mountains and environs
dct_description_sm: Map of the Harz Mountains and environs. Relief shown by hachures. Title supplied by cataloger. Probably issued in: Naturwissenschaftliche Beiträge zur Kenntniss des Harzgebirges, insbesondere der Grafschaft Wernigerode ... / von H.W. Hertzer. Wernigerode : Angerstein, 1856.
dct_publisher_sm: Wernigerode : Lith. Inst. v. B. Angerstein, [1856] ([S.l. : C. Lüders lith.)
